      "seed": 71133229,
      "version": 2,
      "versionNonce": 391234335,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1711000000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "POST /api/conversation/plan\n\n1. Load LearnerModel (CEFR, skills)\n2. Load last session's reviews\n   (IntroducedItems + ErrorLogs)\n3. generateTopic() via Haiku\n   (ONLY LLM call in planning)\n4. Build LessonPlan (5 phases)\n5. Generate 5 pre-built slides\n6. Create Lesson record (DB)\n7. Init RedisSessionState\n8. Return agentMetadata",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": "r1",
      "originalText": "POST /api/conversation/plan\n\n1. Load LearnerModel (CEFR, skills)\n2. Load last session's reviews\n   (IntroducedItems + ErrorLogs)\n3. generateTopic() via Haiku\n   (ONLY LLM call in planning)\n4. Build LessonPlan (5 phases)\n5. Generate 5 pre-built slides\n6. Create Lesson record (DB)\n7. Init RedisSessionState\n8. Return agentMetadata",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
