      "updated": 1711000000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Voice Session (WebRTC)\n\nAgent builds 6-slot system prompt\nPer-turn: Redis state injected\n\n4 tools (all return empty ''):\n  flagError      fire-and-forget\n  writeWhiteboard soft-block 10ms\n  updatePhase    blocking\n  endLesson      blocking+500ms\n\nContext compression > 20 turns",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": "r3",
      "originalText": "Voice Session (WebRTC)\n\nAgent builds 6-slot system prompt\nPer-turn: Redis state injected\n\n4 tools (all return empty ''):\n  flagError      fire-and-forget\n  writeWhiteboard soft-block 10ms\n  updatePhase    blocking\n  endLesson      blocking+500ms\n\nContext compression > 20 turns",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
