      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "POST /api/conversation/end\n\n5-Step Pipeline (resumable):\n  1. Error Classification  (LLM)\n  2. Strength Analysis     (LLM)\n  3. Personal Facts        (LLM)\n  4. CEFR Delta       (NO LLM!)\n  5. Summary Generation    (LLM)\n\npipelineStage for crash resume\nAll steps are idempotent\nSTT artifacts filtered in Step 1",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": "r4",
      "originalText": "POST /api/conversation/end\n\n5-Step Pipeline (resumable):\n  1. Error Classification  (LLM)\n  2. Strength Analysis     (LLM)\n  3. Personal Facts        (LLM)\n  4. CEFR Delta       (NO LLM!)\n  5. Summary Generation    (LLM)\n\npipelineStage for crash resume\nAll steps are idempotent\nSTT artifacts filtered in Step 1",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
