      "text": "6-SLOT SYSTEM PROMPT  (~2000 tokens target)\n\nSlot 1: Identity & Role\n  Persona, voice rules (no markdown, no narration, 1-3 sentences)\n\nSlot 2: Learner Profile  (from agentMetadata)\n  CEFR Grammar/Fluency, name, occupation, family, goals, interests\n  recentUpdates[10] -- ONLY reference facts listed here, never infer\n\nSlot 3: Lesson Plan\n  warmup (questionOfDay + personalHook), review (items or skip),\n  core (topic, angle, targetGrammar), phase time budgets\n\nSlot 4: Phase Instructions\n  Exit criteria per phase, permission protocol\n  (MUST ask before transitioning), one-extension rule\n\nSlot 5: Tool Instructions\n  flagError (minor/major only), updateLessonPhase, endLesson\n\nSlot 6: Behavioral Constraints\n  STT failures, off-script user, disputed corrections,\n  emotional user, hallucination guard, above-level production\n\nPER-TURN ADDENDUM:  Redis state (~80 tokens)\n  Current phase + elapsed, whiteboard, errors, extension status",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": "rpr",
      "originalText": "6-SLOT SYSTEM PROMPT  (~2000 tokens target)\n\nSlot 1: Identity & Role\n  Persona, voice rules (no markdown, no narration, 1-3 sentences)\n\nSlot 2: Learner Profile  (from agentMetadata)\n  CEFR Grammar/Fluency, name, occupation, family, goals, interests\n  recentUpdates[10] -- ONLY reference facts listed here, never infer\n\nSlot 3: Lesson Plan\n  warmup (questionOfDay + personalHook), review (items or skip),\n  core (topic, angle, targetGrammar), phase time budgets\n\nSlot 4: Phase Instructions\n  Exit criteria per phase, permission protocol\n  (MUST ask before transitioning), one-extension rule\n\nSlot 5: Tool Instructions\n  flagError (minor/major only), updateLessonPhase, endLesson\n\nSlot 6: Behavioral Constraints\n  STT failures, off-script user, disputed corrections,\n  emotional user, hallucination guard, above-level production\n\nPER-TURN ADDENDUM:  Redis state (~80 tokens)\n  Current phase + elapsed, whiteboard, errors, extension status",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
