    {
      "id": "tph",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 825,
      "y": 930,
      "width": 603.1999999999999,
      "height": 430.0,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 683966488,
      "version": 2,
      "versionNonce": 1757692517,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1711000000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "LESSON PHASES\n\nWARMUP (5-8m) -> REVIEW (8m / skip) -> CORE (var) -> DEBRIEF (4m) -> CLOSING (3m)\n\nWARMUP exit:   User shared personal update AND 4+ min elapsed.\n               OR 6 min hard cap regardless.\nREVIEW exit:   All review items covered (each attempted once).\n               OR 10 min elapsed. Begin wrapping at 8 min.\nCORE exit:     Topic substantively explored AND 18+ min.\n               OR 25 min hard cap.\nDEBRIEF exit:  Major errors reviewed with correction attempts.\n               OR 5 min elapsed.\nCLOSING:       Terminal. Encourage, preview next, call endLesson.\n\nReview skip rule:\n  No IntroducedItems AND no ErrorLogs from last session\n  -> skip review, redistribute: +3m warmup, +5m core\n\nFirst session (no history):\n  Skip review, extended warmup (7-8m), core = assessment.\n  CEFR starts at 1.0 (A1).\n\nPermission protocol:\n  Agent MUST ask before EVERY transition. Wait for ack.\n\nOne-extension rule:\n  Grant ONE extension (3 min max) if user wants to continue.\n  Second request -> \"let's save for next time\" -> proceed.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": "rph",
      "originalText": "LESSON PHASES\n\nWARMUP (5-8m) -> REVIEW (8m / skip) -> CORE (var) -> DEBRIEF (4m) -> CLOSING (3m)\n\nWARMUP exit:   User shared personal update AND 4+ min elapsed.\n               OR 6 min hard cap regardless.\nREVIEW exit:   All review items covered (each attempted once).\n               OR 10 min elapsed. Begin wrapping at 8 min.\nCORE exit:     Topic substantively explored AND 18+ min.\n               OR 25 min hard cap.\nDEBRIEF exit:  Major errors reviewed with correction attempts.\n               OR 5 min elapsed.\nCLOSING:       Terminal. Encourage, preview next, call endLesson.\n\nReview skip rule:\n  No IntroducedItems AND no ErrorLogs from last session\n  -> skip review, redistribute: +3m warmup, +5m core\n\nFirst session (no history):\n  Skip review, extended warmup (7-8m), core = assessment.\n  CEFR starts at 1.0 (A1).\n\nPermission protocol:\n  Agent MUST ask before EVERY transition. Wait for ack.\n\nOne-extension rule:\n  Grant ONE extension (3 min max) if user wants to continue.\n  Second request -> \"let's save for next time\" -> proceed.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
