      "updated": 1711000000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "POSTGRES (Supabase) -- 10 Models via Prisma\n\nUser\n  Auth, profile (interests, occupation,\n  family, goals, recentUpdates[10]).\n\nLearnerModel  (1:1 with User)\n  cefrGrammar/Fluency (1.0-6.0)\n  skills[21] JSON, sessionCount\n\nProducedItem  (running vocab/grammar bank)\n  type: vocab | grammar, surface,\n  occurrenceCount, unique per user\n  Informs CEFR calc + planning\n\nCurriculumVocab  (reference word list)\n  language, surface, reading, translation\n  cefrLevel, domain. Seeded per language.\n\nCurriculumGrammar  (reference patterns)\n  language, pattern, displayName,\n  cefrLevel, description. Seeded.\n\nIntroducedItem  (tutor-surfaced, per session)\nLesson  (plan, transcript, summary, stage)\nErrorLog  (per-error, session-scoped)\nSubscription   Stripe (free | pro)\nDailyUsage     conversation seconds/day",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": "rdb",
      "originalText": "POSTGRES (Supabase) -- 10 Models via Prisma\n\nUser\n  Auth, profile (interests, occupation,\n  family, goals, recentUpdates[10]).\n\nLearnerModel  (1:1 with User)\n  cefrGrammar/Fluency (1.0-6.0)\n  skills[21] JSON, sessionCount\n\nProducedItem  (running vocab/grammar bank)\n  type: vocab | grammar, surface,\n  occurrenceCount, unique per user\n  Informs CEFR calc + planning\n\nCurriculumVocab  (reference word list)\n  language, surface, reading, translation\n  cefrLevel, domain. Seeded per language.\n\nCurriculumGrammar  (reference patterns)\n  language, pattern, displayName,\n  cefrLevel, description. Seeded.\n\nIntroducedItem  (tutor-surfaced, per session)\nLesson  (plan, transcript, summary, stage)\nErrorLog  (per-error, session-scoped)\nSubscription   Stripe (free | pro)\nDailyUsage     conversation seconds/day",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
