      "seed": 1298588539,
      "version": 2,
      "versionNonce": 1855956496,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1711000000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "REDIS  --  Live Session State\nKey: session:{sessionId}   TTL: 4 hours\n\nRedisSessionState {\n  sessionId: string\n  lessonPlan: LessonPlan\n  currentPhase: LessonPhase\n    // warmup|review|core|debrief|closing\n  phaseStartTimeMs: number\n  phaseExtensionGranted: boolean\n\n  errorsLogged: ErrorLog[]\n    // from flagError tool calls\n  correctionsQueued: ErrorLog[]\n    // subset for debrief + corrections doc\n  vocabIntroduced: string[]\n    // auto-populates whiteboard\n  grammarIntroduced: string[]\n    // auto-populates whiteboard\n  currentSlide: SlideContent\n    // what the learner sees\n}\n\nWHO READS/WRITES:\n  Web (plan)    Write  (initialize)\n  Agent tools   Write  (flagError, phase)\n  Agent turn    Read   (inject to prompt)\n  Web (end)     Read   (pipeline input)\n  Web (end)     Delete (cleanup)\n\nFire-and-forget: appendFlaggedError()\nBlocking: setLessonPhase(), endLesson()",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": "rrd",
      "originalText": "REDIS  --  Live Session State\nKey: session:{sessionId}   TTL: 4 hours\n\nRedisSessionState {\n  sessionId: string\n  lessonPlan: LessonPlan\n  currentPhase: LessonPhase\n    // warmup|review|core|debrief|closing\n  phaseStartTimeMs: number\n  phaseExtensionGranted: boolean\n\n  errorsLogged: ErrorLog[]\n    // from flagError tool calls\n  correctionsQueued: ErrorLog[]\n    // subset for debrief + corrections doc\n  vocabIntroduced: string[]\n    // auto-populates whiteboard\n  grammarIntroduced: string[]\n    // auto-populates whiteboard\n  currentSlide: SlideContent\n    // what the learner sees\n}\n\nWHO READS/WRITES:\n  Web (plan)    Write  (initialize)\n  Agent tools   Write  (flagError, phase)\n  Agent turn    Read   (inject to prompt)\n  Web (end)     Read   (pipeline input)\n  Web (end)     Delete (cleanup)\n\nFire-and-forget: appendFlaggedError()\nBlocking: setLessonPhase(), endLesson()",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "rcf",
