    {
      "id": "tcf",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1075,
      "y": 1450,
      "width": 351.2,
      "height": 565.0,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 622934120,
      "version": 2,
      "versionNonce": 1926786887,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1711000000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "CEFR + SKILLS TRACKING\n\nCEFR: Two independent floats (1.0 - 6.0)\n  A1 = 1.0   A2 = 2.0   B1 = 3.0\n  B2 = 4.0   C1 = 5.0   C2 = 6.0\n\nUpdated ALGORITHMICALLY after each session:\n(Step 4 of pipeline -- NO LLM involved)\n\n  grammarDelta = +0.02  (base)\n    - majorErrors  x 0.04 x minuteScale\n    - minorErrors  x 0.01 x minuteScale\n    + min(vocabProduced x 0.005, 0.04)\n\n  fluencyDelta = +0.02  (base)\n    - l1Switches   x 0.03 x minuteScale\n    - hesitations   x 0.005 x minuteScale\n    + selfCorrects x 0.01 x minuteScale\n    + min(grammarProduced x 0.008, 0.04)\n\n  Both capped at +/-0.15 per session.\n  Produced items from ProducedItem bank\n  give a positive signal for range/diversity.\n\n21 SKILLS (hardcoded enum, no dynamic):\n  introduce_self, greet_farewell,\n  tell_time, describe_location, ...\n  small_talk, argue_a_point, etc.\n\n  Mastery 0=untested 1=struggled\n  2=with support 3=independent 4=auto\n  Updated by post-session Step 2 (LLM)\n  Skills and CEFR are independent systems.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": "rcf",
      "originalText": "CEFR + SKILLS TRACKING\n\nCEFR: Two independent floats (1.0 - 6.0)\n  A1 = 1.0   A2 = 2.0   B1 = 3.0\n  B2 = 4.0   C1 = 5.0   C2 = 6.0\n\nUpdated ALGORITHMICALLY after each session:\n(Step 4 of pipeline -- NO LLM involved)\n\n  grammarDelta = +0.02  (base)\n    - majorErrors  x 0.04 x minuteScale\n    - minorErrors  x 0.01 x minuteScale\n    + min(vocabProduced x 0.005, 0.04)\n\n  fluencyDelta = +0.02  (base)\n    - l1Switches   x 0.03 x minuteScale\n    - hesitations   x 0.005 x minuteScale\n    + selfCorrects x 0.01 x minuteScale\n    + min(grammarProduced x 0.008, 0.04)\n\n  Both capped at +/-0.15 per session.\n  Produced items from ProducedItem bank\n  give a positive signal for range/diversity.\n\n21 SKILLS (hardcoded enum, no dynamic):\n  introduce_self, greet_farewell,\n  tell_time, describe_location, ...\n  small_talk, argue_a_point, etc.\n\n  Mastery 0=untested 1=struggled\n  2=with support 3=independent 4=auto\n  Updated by post-session Step 2 (LLM)\n  Skills and CEFR are independent systems.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
