      "text": "lingle/\n+-- apps/\n|   +-- web/  (@lingle/web)  --  Next.js 15 + React 19 + Tailwind CSS\n|   |   +-- app/api/conversation/plan/     Session planning (1 Haiku LLM call)\n|   |   +-- app/api/conversation/end/      Post-session pipeline (4 Haiku LLM calls)\n|   |   +-- app/api/voice/                 LiveKit token + agent dispatch\n|   |   +-- app/(app)/dashboard/           Home, CEFR display, start session\n|   |   +-- app/(app)/conversation/voice/  Session flow (plan -> voice -> summary)\n|   |   +-- components/voice/              VoiceAuraOrb, LiveKitBridge, Whiteboard, DevTools\n|   |   +-- components/session/            SessionView (state machine), SessionSummary\n|   |   +-- lib/\n|   |       +-- post-session-pipeline.ts   5-step analysis pipeline\n|   |       +-- cefr-updater.ts            Deterministic CEFR formula (no LLM)\n|   |       +-- redis.ts                   Web-side Redis client (read/write/delete)\n|   |       +-- usage-guard.ts             Rate limiting (free=60m/day, pro=unlimited)\n|   |\n|   +-- agent/ (@lingle/agent)  --  LiveKit Agents SDK (pure Node.js, no React)\n|       +-- src/\n|           +-- index.ts                   Worker entry: VAD, STT, TTS, LLM setup\n|           +-- lingle-agent.ts            6-slot system prompt + context compression\n|           +-- tools.ts                   4 tools: flagError, writeWhiteboard, updateLessonPhase, endLesson\n|           +-- session-state.ts           Redis CRUD + serializeForPrompt()\n|           +-- claude-llm.ts              Anthropic SDK adapter, prompt caching\n|           +-- cartesia-tts.ts            Persistent WebSocket TTS (CJK fast/natural modes)\n|           +-- rime-tts.ts                Rime TTS (English optimized)\n|           +-- soniox-stt.ts              Soniox streaming STT (multilingual)\n|           +-- config.ts                  Provider resolution + language maps\n|\n+-- packages/\n|   +-- shared/ (@lingle/shared)           TypeScript types, Skill enum (21), cefrLabel()\n|   +-- db/     (@lingle/db)               Prisma client singleton\n|\n+-- prisma/schema.prisma                   10 models: User, LearnerModel, IntroducedItem,\n                                           ProducedItem, IntroducedItem, Lesson,\n                                           ErrorLog, Subscription, DailyUsage",
